{
    "chapter": [
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "He frowned and turned away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "because the blind man came to him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "And how would you know, he may purify himself"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "or take notice, so the reminder would benefit him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "But whoever supposes he has no need"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "then you pay attention to him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "while it is not your responsibility if he did not purify"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "But whoever comes to you rushing"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "and he fears (God)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "then you pay no attention to him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "No way, it (Quran) is a reminder"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "and anyone who wants takes notice from it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "In honored scriptures"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "elevated and purified"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "by the hands of ambassadors/scribes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "noble and good"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Damn the human being, how ungrateful he is"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "What did He create him from"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "He created him from a fertilized egg (Zygote), then proportioned him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "Then He made the way easy for him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "Then He made him die and had him buried"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Then He raises him when He wants"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "No way, he did not fulfill what He ordered him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "So the human being should look at his food"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Indeed We poured the rain as shower"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "then We split open the earth as cracks"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "then We made grain grow in it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "and grapes and vegetable"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "and olive and date"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "and fenced gardens with lots of trees"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 31,
            "text": "and fruit and grass"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 32,
            "text": "an enjoyment for you and your livestock"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 33,
            "text": "So when the deafening blast comes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 34,
            "text": "a day when the man runs away from his brother"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 35,
            "text": "and his mother and his father"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 36,
            "text": "and his spouse and his sons (children)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 37,
            "text": "on that day every one of them has an issue occupying him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 38,
            "text": "On that day (some) faces are bright"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 39,
            "text": "laughing and joyful"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 40,
            "text": "And on that day (other) faces have dust on them"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 41,
            "text": "darkness covers it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 42,
            "text": "they are the disbelievers, the immoral ones"
        }
    ]
}